{"tid":123539,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<捉完放左再捉>Samsung 掌門人李在鎔因行賄被批捕","createTime":"2017-02-17T02:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T03:00:28.000Z","uid":45285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0029e293ba6ad85887b910eab25a0b3ec2e9f1a2","tid":123539,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:34:39.000Z","msg":"據彭博社報導，Samsung 目前的實際掌權人、副會長李在鎔已於日前被南韓法院批捕。早在一月初時，特別檢查組就曾提交過逮捕的申請，但當時法院因證據不足並沒有批准逮捕令。而後檢方再次以隱瞞非法收入、違法轉移資產出國為由提出第二輪指控，這次法院終於做出了支持他們的決定。<br />\n<br />\n在被批捕之後，李在鎔將會先被收入拘留所，之後的庭審和裁決可能要花最多 18 個月的時間。Samsung 方面，則表示會盡全力讓真相「水落石出」。但要是最終結果不利的話，高層動盪不光是對這家企業，對整個南韓的經濟可能都會造成非常大的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/02/16/samsungs-south-korean-leader-has-been-arrested/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2017%2F02%2F16%2Fsamsungs-south-korean-leader-has-been-arrested%2F&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=d4d9788a\" target=\"_blank\">http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/02/16/samsungs-south-korean-leader-has-been-arrested/</a>"},{"pid":"640d8629bcce5825a6f5c24ba51cebf985fc9838","tid":123539,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"Samsung佔韓國經濟咁大比率<br />\n檢察組咁夠膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c3c2e85b3afb3dd3d7a2fc9526bfc2059aa92e","tid":123539,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"Shamesung 無打手，Shamesung 好廉潔，Shamesung 係正義之師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01138a723c08adc2f34600e0986dd5e367ecacfd","tid":123539,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:47:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da1956f8502c6cc96c435472602c68a1f13456f2","tid":123539,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:57:44.000Z